command: from lifesim.types import Position, Agent, WorldState; p = Position(row=0, col=0); a = Agent(energy=10, age=0, direction=0); ws = WorldState(width=5, height=5, step_number=0, seed=42, agents=((p, a),)); assert ws.width == 5 and len(ws.agents) == 1

from lifesim.types import StepResult, TickMetrics, SimConfig, WorldState; ws = WorldState(5, 5, 0, 42, ()); sr = StepResult(world=ws, births=0, deaths=0, movements=0); tm = TickMetrics(step_number=0, population=0, births=0, deaths=0, avg_energy=0.0); sc = SimConfig(width=10, height=10, seed=42); assert sc.initial_density == 0.3 and sc.max_steps == 100
